{"Version": "1.0.0", "LINES": [{"text": "Greta and Jan Navel quit their\njobs in 2021 and bought a used SUV.", "start": 22.72, "duration": 5.4, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Greta"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "2021"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "A study showed that in 2021,", "start": 161.44, "duration": 2.48, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2021"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "twenty-five percent of people\nwere open to the idea of a new job.", "start": 163.92, "duration": 3.96, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "twenty-five percent"}], "sentiment": 0.06818181818181818}, {"text": "In 2022, that number\nrose to thirty-seven percent.", "start": 168.32, "duration": 3.16, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2022"}, {"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "thirty-seven percent"}], "sentiment": 0.6}, {"text": "Trumpf is one of the world's biggest\nmanufacturers of machine-tools.", "start": 229.08, "duration": 4.28, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Three shirts,\nwashed and pressed.", "start": 244.92, "duration": 1.8, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "Three"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "One-fifty per shirt.", "start": 250.4, "duration": 1.6, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "One-fifty"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Employees pay one-euro-fifty\nfor washing and ironing", "start": 255.56, "duration": 3.48, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "fifty"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "a big help for the\n43-year-old and his family.", "start": 260.32, "duration": 2.6, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "43-year-old"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Pascal Janikovits was an\napprentice here 26 years ago.", "start": 268.24, "duration": 3.52, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Pascal Janikovits"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "26 years ago"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The machine operator\nused to watch one machine.", "start": 275.92, "duration": 2.8, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "These days, one operator\nlooks after two or three.", "start": 283.44, "duration": 3.12, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "These days"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "two or three"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The family-owned German company\nemploys around 15,000 worldwide.", "start": 304.12, "duration": 4.24, "ents": [{"label_": "NORP", "text": "German"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "around 15,000"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "at least 15 hours a\nweek or a maximum of 40.", "start": 328.72, "duration": 2.84, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "at least 15 hours"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "40"}], "sentiment": -0.3}, {"text": "She's only twelve, so we didn\u00edt\nwant to leave her alone all day.", "start": 349.76, "duration": 2.64, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "only twelve"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "all day"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Family is important\nfor the 43-year-old.", "start": 354.92, "duration": 1.92, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "43-year-old"}], "sentiment": 0.4}, {"text": "not full time, but\nabout 80-percent.", "start": 368.44, "duration": 2.08, "ents": [], "sentiment": -0.175}, {"text": "For him, good\nconditions are one thing,", "start": 386.96, "duration": 1.92, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.7}, {"text": "but Trumpf has had flexible\nschedules for 15-years.", "start": 423.96, "duration": 3.2, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "15-years"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The take-out food\ncosts between two and", "start": 447.96, "duration": 2.2, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "between two and"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "five euros and can\nmake life easier.", "start": 450.16, "duration": 2.6, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "five"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Eighty-five percent of\nsurvey respondents thing", "start": 500.48, "duration": 2.56, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "Eighty-five percent"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Flexible working hours\nwere a factor for 79-percent.", "start": 507.6, "duration": 2.92, "ents": [{"label_": "TIME", "text": "hours"}, {"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "79-percent"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "And for 73-percent, the\nstarting salary was also key.", "start": 511.4, "duration": 3.52, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "73-percent"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Pascal ends his workday\nwith two hours of overtime,", "start": 595.32, "duration": 2.88, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "workday"}, {"label_": "TIME", "text": "two hours"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "After 26 years, he feels\nconnected to his employer.", "start": 616.36, "duration": 3.52, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "26 years"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In a 2020 survey,", "start": 625.2, "duration": 1.68, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2020"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "only 17% of respondents said", "start": 626.88, "duration": 2.88, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "only 17%"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Eighty-three percent\nfelt none at all.", "start": 633.68, "duration": 1.96, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "Eighty-three percent"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Ali Mahlodji is a 41-year-old\nentrepreneur from Vienna.", "start": 657.36, "duration": 3.44, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Ali Mahlodji"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "41-year-old"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Vienna"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "At 27, I was the youngest\nperson in the role in Europe.", "start": 699.32, "duration": 2.88, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "27"}, {"label_": "LOC", "text": "Europe"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "I as a 40-year-old might learn\nmore about digital innovation", "start": 770.64, "duration": 3.36, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "40-year-old"}], "sentiment": 0.25}, {"text": "from a 16-year-old\nthan they would from me.", "start": 774.0, "duration": 1.88, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "16-year-old"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Let's drive to this town\nabout fifteen minutes away,", "start": 859.24, "duration": 2.12, "ents": [{"label_": "TIME", "text": "about fifteen minutes"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "around 15 hours a week.", "start": 874.2, "duration": 1.68, "ents": [{"label_": "TIME", "text": "around 15 hours"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "based about 2,000 kilometers\naway in Landau in western Germany.", "start": 904.8, "duration": 3.96, "ents": [{"label_": "QUANTITY", "text": "about 2,000 kilometers"}, {"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Landau"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Germany"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Four and a half years ago, Greta\nand I got engaged on Kilimanjaro.", "start": 981.08, "duration": 3.72, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "Four and a half years ago"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "Greta"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "Kilimanjaro"}], "sentiment": -0.16666666666666666}, {"text": "for example, the daily maximum\nworking time of eight hours", "start": 1195.08, "duration": 3.08, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "daily"}, {"label_": "TIME", "text": "eight hours"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "with eleven hours of rest.", "start": 1198.16, "duration": 1.52, "ents": [{"label_": "TIME", "text": "eleven hours"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In 2019, just under 13-percent of\nthe workforce worked from home.", "start": 1204.2, "duration": 4.64, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2019"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In 2021, that number\nwas 25-percent.", "start": 1209.88, "duration": 2.92, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2021"}, {"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "25-percent"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "And more than half - 56-percent", "start": 1214.52, "duration": 2.68, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "more than half - 56-percent"}], "sentiment": 0.16666666666666669}, {"text": "Twenty-five party\nrolls for Saturday.", "start": 1292.44, "duration": 2.16, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "Twenty-five"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "Saturday"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Steffen Leonhardt took it\nover from his parents in 2009.", "start": 1338.76, "duration": 3.92, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Steffen Leonhardt"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "2009"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "That was the first problem.", "start": 1360.2, "duration": 1.96, "ents": [{"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "first"}], "sentiment": 0.25}, {"text": "He\u00eds been looking after\nits channel for two years.", "start": 1419.68, "duration": 2.72, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "two years"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Getting back in the black helped\nLeonhardt solve the second problem:", "start": 1442.96, "duration": 3.96, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Leonhardt"}, {"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "second"}], "sentiment": -0.05555555555555555}, {"text": "between nine and\neleven euros per hour.", "start": 1450.56, "duration": 2.16, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "between nine"}, {"label_": "PRODUCT", "text": "eleven euros"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Today, we start in\nsales at 12 or 12.50.", "start": 1457.56, "duration": 2.6, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "Today"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "12"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "12.50"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In the bakery it\u00eds 13.50 or !4,\ndepending on qualifications.", "start": 1461.04, "duration": 4.24, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "13.50"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "4"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "That leaves the third problem:", "start": 1467.0, "duration": 1.8, "ents": [{"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "third"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Leonhardt tackled that one\ntogether with his wife, Stefanie.", "start": 1473.08, "duration": 3.32, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Leonhardt"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Stefanie"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Stefanie Leonhardt\nintroduced a four-day week.", "start": 1489.76, "duration": 2.88, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Stefanie Leonhardt"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "four-day week"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Then four people are on vacation\nfrom Sunday and three before that.", "start": 1507.92, "duration": 3.28, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "four"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "Sunday"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "three"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "You never get\n100-percent satisfaction.", "start": 1527.04, "duration": 2.68, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "100-percent"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "What\u00eds perfect for one person\nmight mean that another person", "start": 1536.84, "duration": 3.32, "ents": [{"label_": "ORG", "text": "What\u00eds"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.34375}, {"text": "has a shift when they\u00edd\nrather not have one.", "start": 1540.16, "duration": 2.24, "ents": [{"label_": "ORG", "text": "they\u00edd\n"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Heiko Larig has worked\nas a baker for 26 years,", "start": 1556.76, "duration": 3.6, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Heiko Larig"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "26 years"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "getting up around 3\na.m. almost every day.", "start": 1560.52, "duration": 3.04, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "almost every day"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "to go to bed at 8\nor 7 every night.", "start": 1577.56, "duration": 1.88, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "8"}, {"label_": "TIME", "text": "7 every night"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "No one knows\nwhere it\u00edll take us next.", "start": 1603.72, "duration": 1.76, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In the mid-19th century, working up to\n80 hours a week was considered normal.", "start": 1661.36, "duration": 4.88, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "the mid-19th century"}], "sentiment": 0.15}, {"text": "At the turn of the century, the\nsix-day week was introduced,", "start": 1666.32, "duration": 3.44, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "the turn of the century"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "six-day week"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "with a ten-hour day.", "start": 1669.76, "duration": 1.24, "ents": [{"label_": "TIME", "text": "ten-hour"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In 1918, the eight-hour\nday became the norm.", "start": 1671.44, "duration": 3.36, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "1918"}, {"label_": "TIME", "text": "eight-hour"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Physical stress hasn\u00edt\ndecreased in the last 20 years.", "start": 1709.0, "duration": 2.96, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "the last 20 years"}], "sentiment": -0.13333333333333333}, {"text": "In 2020, 35-percent of surveyed\nworkers experienced burn-out.", "start": 1731.84, "duration": 4.72, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2020"}, {"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "35-percent"}], "sentiment": 0.8}, {"text": "In 2021, the figure was\neven higher, 38-percent.", "start": 1738.32, "duration": 5.04, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2021"}, {"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "38-percent"}], "sentiment": 0.25}, {"text": "there were nearly 900 million\nhours of unpaid overtime.", "start": 1773.52, "duration": 3.08, "ents": [{"label_": "MONEY", "text": "900 million\nhours"}], "sentiment": 0.15000000000000002}, {"text": "The water tank is just one upgrade\nwe\u00edve done here in Germany.", "start": 1824.8, "duration": 3.16, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Germany"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "We\u00edll have an additional 25\nliters of water to use on board.", "start": 1828.76, "duration": 3.64, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "We\u00edll"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The more-than three months\nliving and working on the road", "start": 1837.56, "duration": 2.72, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "-than three months"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "After all, they\u00edre business\nconsultants working two days a week,", "start": 1864.16, "duration": 3.36, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "two days a week"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "They\u00edre living space amounts\nto just under eight square meters.", "start": 1889.64, "duration": 3.44, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "just under eight square meters"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Two forks, two spoons, two\nknives, two small spoons, that's it.", "start": 1903.08, "duration": 3.64, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "Two"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "two"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "two"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "two"}], "sentiment": -0.25}, {"text": "The car is 99% done.", "start": 1983.48, "duration": 2.16, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "99%"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "As of a few weeks ago, she she\u00eds\nbeen working four days a week", "start": 2004.04, "duration": 3.8, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "a few weeks ago"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "four days"}], "sentiment": -0.2}, {"text": "instead of five.", "start": 2007.84, "duration": 0.96, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "five"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Normally, I have to be out\nof the house by seven-thirty.", "start": 2033.92, "duration": 2.64, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "seven-thirty"}], "sentiment": 0.15}, {"text": "One fewer day at the hotel has\nother advantages for the 23-year-old.", "start": 2041.36, "duration": 4.28, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "One"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "23-year-old"}], "sentiment": -0.125}, {"text": "When she told me she had\nthe opportunity to work four days,", "start": 2066.56, "duration": 2.92, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "four days"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "She was actually a\nlittle skeptical at first.", "start": 2071.44, "duration": 2.2, "ents": [{"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "first"}], "sentiment": -0.14583333333333334}, {"text": "Annemarie works here, at\nthe \"25 Hours\" hotel in Cologne.", "start": 2078.16, "duration": 3.56, "ents": [{"label_": "TIME", "text": "the \"25 Hours"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Cologne"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The company that runs the hotel\nrecently introduced the four-day week.", "start": 2086.6, "duration": 4.08, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "four-day week"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Annemarie\u00eds been working\nat the hotel for four years.", "start": 2117.44, "duration": 3.04, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "four years"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Our shift times have changed since\nthe four-day week was introduced.", "start": 2129.2, "duration": 3.76, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "four-day week"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "We now work nine hours\nwith a 45-minute break.", "start": 2133.48, "duration": 2.88, "ents": [{"label_": "TIME", "text": "nine hours"}, {"label_": "TIME", "text": "45-minute"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Sometimes just eight hours is\ndemanding, and now it\u00eds nine.", "start": 2142.48, "duration": 3.04, "ents": [{"label_": "TIME", "text": "just eight hours"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "nine"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The hotel group has about\n700 employees in Germany.", "start": 2149.0, "duration": 3.52, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "700"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Germany"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The four-day week is already in\nother industries and other areas.", "start": 2173.72, "duration": 2.84, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "four-day week"}], "sentiment": -0.125}, {"text": "Staff now get three\ndays off a week", "start": 2184.12, "duration": 2.4, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "three\ndays"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The 26-year-old has\nyet to find a drawback.", "start": 2191.08, "duration": 2.44, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "26-year-old"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "It\u00eds logical that we need more staff\nbecause there\u00eds one day missing,", "start": 2235.04, "duration": 3.52, "ents": [{"label_": "ORG", "text": "It\u00eds"}], "sentiment": 0.18333333333333335}, {"text": "in three departments we aren\u00edt\nyet able to offer a four-day week,", "start": 2242.32, "duration": 3.4, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "three"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "four-day week"}], "sentiment": 0.5}, {"text": "But the four-day\nmodel is up and running", "start": 2251.92, "duration": 2.28, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "four-day"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "in five of the hotel's\neight departments anyway.", "start": 2254.2, "duration": 2.32, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "five"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "eight"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "the four-day work week is a\nchallenge for the company.", "start": 2275.48, "duration": 2.76, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "four-day"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "There\u00eds this 1 o'clock\nslump, where normally", "start": 2304.52, "duration": 2.72, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.15}, {"text": "with the five-day\nweek you\u00edd be finished.", "start": 2307.24, "duration": 1.8, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "five-day\nweek"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Children born today have a life\nexpectancy of at least 85 to 90 years.", "start": 2399.0, "duration": 5.24, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "today"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "at least 85"}], "sentiment": -0.3}, {"text": "Like having more time away\nfrom work between 20 and 30,", "start": 2414.0, "duration": 3.0, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "between 20 and 30"}], "sentiment": 0.5}, {"text": "then in return working\nmore between 50 and 70.", "start": 2417.0, "duration": 2.88, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "between 50 and 70"}], "sentiment": 0.5}, {"text": "And I think it\u00edll come in\nthe next five or six years.", "start": 2422.08, "duration": 2.4, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "What I\u00edve gained by giving that\nup is to work for a start-up for one.", "start": 2462.52, "duration": 3.92, "ents": [{"label_": "NORP", "text": "I\u00edve"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "So that\u00eds one thing.", "start": 2474.76, "duration": 1.36, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Those are the three things I\ngot when I traded in the old job.", "start": 2492.8, "duration": 2.72, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "three"}], "sentiment": 0.1}, {"text": "No one knows what\nthe future holds.", "start": 2509.72, "duration": 2.08, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}], "VIDEO_ID": "W_4OS-1x_A0", "VIDEO_DATA": [{"videoId": "W_4OS-1x_A0", "channelId": "UCW39zufHfsuGgpLviKh297Q", "description": "Greta and Jan Navel are living their dream: New Work. They're salaried employees on a world trip by bus. They work wherever ...", "title": "New work - The future of toil | DW Documentary", "publishedAt": "2023-04-28T16:00:33Z"}, {"videoId": "mBtwfaoZa_U", "channelId": "UCW39zufHfsuGgpLviKh297Q", "description": "Pakistan's Sindh region is one of the cradles of human civilization. It's seen as the homeland of the Indus Valley Civilization, ...", "title": "Pakistan\u2019s forgotten civilization | DW Documentary", "publishedAt": "2023-04-28T14:00:36Z"}]}